Women who are already over 40, are sometimes not "marriage material" for older men. They are afraid that if they are too nice to her, then she is likely to cheat on a long contract.

Also, a new lover who is about the same age or short several years younger, should not expect Martha to ask for her share of the inheritance. Therefore they search for a young partner who would have time to make babies and get them to raise them.

She can make the men’s life rich

"Bitches" in German pensioners' parlance, women who understand how to stroke a man's ego, will find an irrefutable partner. Older women frequently are endowed with a deep sense of sensuality.

They are adept at creating a romantic atmosphere and being ardent lovers and to be the sure welfare for the old age of their partner. Endowed with mature wisdom, they know how to satisfy their male partner.

Women, they say, also have different priorities. Less focus on themselves and more on the "benefits" of the men around them. Sex in the old days had meaning, joy and love. Today, many older women have the time and money to enjoy pleasures with seductive older men.
